subject: Golf
Greenbrier Classic (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Johnson Wagner shot a six-under-par 64 to take a two-stroke lead after the third round of the Greenbrier Classic. Jimmy Walker also shot a 64 and was second at 12 under.
